nodes.text: Kel Plath is a location in Sodonna. New owners of Kel Plath renamed it River Gardens. Kel Plath was a commonal, meaning it was a walled and gated enclosure with residences and a common green space inside. A security droid guarded the gate. There was Fallanassi writing on the walls near the front gate. Luke Skywalker and Akanah Norand Goss Pell visited here in search of Fallanassi.
